                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504328345606-18bbc8c9d7d1?w=600&q=80"
                        alt="Civil Engineering">
                    <div class="faculty-overlay"></div>

                </div>
                <div class="faculty-body">
                    <h3>Civil Engineering</h3>
                    <p class="truncate-text">Designing sustainable infrastructure and structures. Specializations in
                        structural,
                        geotechnical, and water
                        resources engineering.Designing sustainable infrastructure and structures. Specializations in
                        structural,
                        geotechnical, and water
                        resources engineering.</p>
                    <div class="event-meta" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
